text: Frigyes Hollósi (18 February 1906 - 15 January 1979), also known as Hollósi- Jung, was a Hungarian swimmer and rower. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. He also competed in the men's coxed eight in rowing at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1906 births Category:1979 deaths Category:Hungarian male swimmers Category:Hungarian male rowers Category:Olympic swimmers of Hungary Category:Olympic rowers of Hungary Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:People from Nagymaros Category:European Rowing Championships medalists
